-- 02_revenue_by_attribution_channel.sql
WITH latest_channel AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel
  FROM customer_channels
  WHERE (customer_id, attributed_at) IN (
    SELECT customer_id, MAX(attributed_at)
    FROM customer_channels
    GROUP BY customer_id
  )
),
transactions_with_attribution AS (
  SELECT 
    t.transaction_id,
    t.customer_id,
    t.store_id,
    t.amount,
    t.transaction_date,
    COALESCE(lc.channel, 'Unattributed') as channel,
    s.city
  FROM transactions t
  LEFT JOIN latest_channel lc ON t.customer_id = lc.customer_id
  LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
)
SELECT 
  channel,
  COALESCE(city, 'Unknown') as city,
  SUM(amount) as total_revenue,
  COUNT(transaction_id) as transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) as unique_customers
FROM transactions_with_attribution
GROUP BY channel, city
ORDER BY channel, city
